WEBVTT

00:10.211 --> 00:13.145
This man is insane.

00:13.147 --> 00:15.948
He's a predator.
He should have gone to hell.

00:15.950 --> 00:18.617
- It really freaked me out.
- I just want it gone.

00:18.619 --> 00:22.488
I see a war.

00:22.490 --> 00:23.689
What a horrible way to go.

00:23.691 --> 00:26.091
You're my last hope.

00:26.093 --> 00:27.960
He likes them young.

00:27.962 --> 00:30.896
He needs to get the hell
out of my house.

00:30.898 --> 00:34.333
They're absorbing
way too much dead energy.

00:34.335 --> 00:36.869
This is not a good situation.

00:36.871 --> 00:38.737
My name is Amy Allan.

00:38.739 --> 00:40.339
There's death here.

00:40.341 --> 00:42.074
Don't wanna go down there.

00:42.076 --> 00:43.342
I see dead people.

00:43.344 --> 00:45.444
They hide in the walls
and they watch.

00:45.446 --> 00:48.113
I speak to dead people...

00:48.115 --> 00:50.916
She's definitely
a serial killer.

00:50.918 --> 00:52.718
...and they speak to me.

00:52.720 --> 00:54.887
She's going to torture them.

00:54.889 --> 00:58.690
But there's only one way to know
if my findings are real.

00:58.692 --> 01:00.826
They were all murdered.

01:00.828 --> 01:02.327
I rely on my partner.

01:02.329 --> 01:03.896
I'm Steve Di Schiavi.

01:03.898 --> 01:05.697
I'm a retired New York City
homicide detective.

01:05.699 --> 01:08.400
So is this the only time
you've been physically attacked?

01:08.402 --> 01:11.970
And I know every person,
every house has secrets.

01:11.972 --> 01:16.041
There's no question in my mind
that he was talking about Satan.

01:16.043 --> 01:17.743
It's my job to reveal them.

01:17.745 --> 01:19.378
Who do you think
possessed you?

01:19.380 --> 01:21.547
But Steve and I
never speak...

01:21.549 --> 01:23.582
We never communicate
during an investigation.

01:23.584 --> 01:24.817
...until the very end.

01:24.819 --> 01:26.452
Well, you're not gonna want
to see this.

01:26.454 --> 01:28.520
When we uncover if it's safe
for you to stay...

01:28.522 --> 01:30.022
<i>Hell,</i> no.

01:30.024 --> 01:31.690
Or time to get out.

01:31.692 --> 01:33.692
Everyone is in jeopardy.

