01:47.241 --> 01:49.341
I'm in the small town
of Briceville, Tennessee.

01:49.343 --> 01:51.910
It's about a half-hour north
of Knoxville.

01:51.912 --> 01:54.213
I got a call from
a single mom named Leonora.

01:54.215 --> 01:56.715
Now, this poor woman
scrimped and saved to buy

01:56.717 --> 01:58.550
a dream house
for her three kids.

01:58.552 --> 01:59.885
Now here's the problem --

01:59.887 --> 02:01.887
they're all being pushed,
scratched,

02:01.889 --> 02:03.789
and basically scared to death.

02:03.791 --> 02:05.357
She says if we can't help,

02:05.359 --> 02:07.493
someone is going to
wind up badly hurt.

02:13.133 --> 02:14.633
Before Amy arrives,

02:14.635 --> 02:18.403
I clear the area
of any leading information.

02:18.405 --> 02:21.340
This home has a lot
of photographs

02:21.342 --> 02:23.609
and religious symbols,

02:23.611 --> 02:27.913
so it's important that I cover
or remove them all.

02:27.915 --> 02:30.916
When I'm done, the location will
be ready for tonight's walk.

02:41.762 --> 02:43.295
Boy.

02:43.297 --> 02:46.164
I'm just hearing, like,
"Don't come down here."

02:46.166 --> 02:48.267
It's an older male.

02:48.269 --> 02:52.104
He doesn't want living
or dead out here.

02:55.509 --> 03:00.479
He's saying, "Mine. Mine.
Mine. Mine. It's all mine."

03:00.481 --> 03:02.347
How would he affect
the living?

03:02.349 --> 03:08.153
I think, with him, it would be
impressing upon them emotions

03:08.155 --> 03:11.323
of fear and urgency to get out.

03:11.325 --> 03:17.396
This man is completely,
utterly insane.

03:25.673 --> 03:27.973
So, Leonora, you sounded
terrified on the phone.

03:27.975 --> 03:29.908
What are you guys
going through?

03:29.910 --> 03:31.944
I feel like something
is evil here.

03:31.946 --> 03:34.279
It's attacking my family.

03:34.281 --> 03:36.248
It's targeting my kids.

03:36.250 --> 03:39.017
I don't know what to do
to protect them.

03:39.019 --> 03:41.086
How long have you guys
been living here?

03:41.088 --> 03:42.821
I've been here
a little over a year.

03:42.823 --> 03:44.122
Do you know anything
about the history

03:44.124 --> 03:45.557
of the house
or the property?

03:45.559 --> 03:47.392
I was told by a neighbor

03:47.394 --> 03:50.529
that the previous owners
had passed away.

03:50.531 --> 03:52.431
- In the house?
- Yes.

03:52.433 --> 03:54.166
That's something
I'll look into.

03:54.168 --> 03:55.801
Who exactly
lives in the house?

03:55.803 --> 03:58.070
I have a photo.

03:58.072 --> 04:00.973
This is my 14-year-old son,
William.

04:00.975 --> 04:05.043
This is me, my 20-year-old
daughter, Amber.

04:05.045 --> 04:08.480
This is my 4-year-old son,
Easton.

04:08.482 --> 04:13.151
I adopted him to make sure
he had a safe place to go,

04:13.153 --> 04:17.089
and I do not feel like
he has a safe place here.

04:17.091 --> 04:20.492
Easton is being targeted.

04:20.494 --> 04:23.362
He sees things that
we can't explain.

04:23.364 --> 04:25.998
It's getting
very physical with him.

04:26.000 --> 04:27.599
That's got to be hard
on you as a mom.

04:27.601 --> 04:29.434
It's a little
heartbreaking for me.

04:29.436 --> 04:30.802
Do me a favor.

04:30.804 --> 04:33.405
Give me a list of what's
going on as far as activity.

04:33.407 --> 04:35.340
We have everything.

04:35.342 --> 04:40.145
There's been footsteps,
feeling watched, items moving,

04:40.147 --> 04:41.647
shadow figures,

04:41.649 --> 04:45.350
constant nausea,
and physical attacks.

04:45.352 --> 04:46.551
I've got to ask you
a question.

04:46.553 --> 04:47.753
Why don't you just
pick up and leave?

04:47.755 --> 04:49.955
Moving is not an option.

04:49.957 --> 04:52.891
I've poured every bit
of life savings in this home.

04:52.893 --> 04:56.728
What are you hoping to get
out of this investigation?

04:56.730 --> 05:01.066
My family to be safe and go back
to the way it used to be

05:01.068 --> 05:04.069
before we were being
assaulted.

05:04.071 --> 05:07.272
The kids are afraid,
so that breaks my heart.

05:07.274 --> 05:09.875
What do you think is in
this house? What's it want?

05:09.877 --> 05:12.244
I believe it wants to tear
our family apart,

05:12.246 --> 05:15.514
and I believe that it wants us
out of the house.

05:19.753 --> 05:21.920
There's something wrong.

05:21.922 --> 05:24.723
The old dead guy,

05:24.725 --> 05:28.026
he particularly
likes to bother children.

05:30.197 --> 05:32.931
He does call them rug rats,

05:32.933 --> 05:36.802
and he says they are like rats.

05:36.804 --> 05:38.370
They're pests.

05:38.372 --> 05:42.607
And he's very grumpy.
He's very angry.

05:42.609 --> 05:44.943
He will get into...rages.

05:44.945 --> 05:49.114
When he's in a...mood,
he stomps, like...

05:51.118 --> 05:52.984
The whole house will shake.

05:52.986 --> 05:57.389
The living, with him,
would definitely hear

05:57.391 --> 06:01.493
stomping all throughout
the house.

06:06.366 --> 06:08.834
Okay, Leonora, what's going on
in this hallway?

06:08.836 --> 06:12.437
Footsteps coming up and down
the hallway almost nightly.

06:12.439 --> 06:13.839
All right.

06:13.841 --> 06:14.973
So when you hear these steps,
what's it sound like?

06:14.975 --> 06:17.776
I would say it sounds
like a heavier man

06:17.778 --> 06:19.711
stomping down the hallway.

06:19.713 --> 06:21.646
You sure it's nobody that got up
in the middle of the night?

06:21.648 --> 06:26.952
No, because I've got up and
checked, and nothing is there.

06:26.954 --> 06:28.687
Okay. What else?

06:28.689 --> 06:31.256
When I'm laying in
my bedroom at night,

06:31.258 --> 06:33.892
I see a very tall
dark figure of a man

06:33.894 --> 06:36.161
moving up
and down the hallway.

06:36.163 --> 06:37.629
What makes you say
it's a man?

06:37.631 --> 06:39.865
Just the way it's built.
It's really tall.

06:39.867 --> 06:42.501
It's a lot taller
than anybody in the house.

06:42.503 --> 06:44.035
So could it be somebody
on the outside

06:44.037 --> 06:46.037
walking back and forth?
- No.

06:46.039 --> 06:48.173
I keep the blinds shut
all the time.

06:48.175 --> 06:49.608
All right. Anything else?

06:49.610 --> 06:55.180
In the living room, a flashlight
flew off of the coffee table.

06:55.182 --> 06:57.149
Gave me chills.

06:57.151 --> 06:58.416
Couldn't it have just
rolled off?

06:58.418 --> 07:02.020
It is completely square.
There's no way it can roll off.

07:02.022 --> 07:04.589
The scary part is
if it could do that,

07:04.591 --> 07:05.857
it could have
flung it at your head.

07:05.859 --> 07:07.559
Who's to say they won't
pick it up and throw it

07:07.561 --> 07:09.427
at Easton,
being so young?

07:09.429 --> 07:11.530
You know, it could kill him.

07:15.269 --> 07:18.203
This old man,
I'm trying to get out of him

07:18.205 --> 07:20.639
all the...that he does
to the living.

07:20.641 --> 07:22.908
Do they see him?

07:22.910 --> 07:26.945
I think they do see him
when he's pitching a fit.

07:26.947 --> 07:29.347
Why do you get mad?

07:29.349 --> 07:31.383
I'm seeing him getting mad

07:31.385 --> 07:34.419
and throwing things
around violently.

07:36.890 --> 07:39.791
He's showing me plates flying.

07:39.793 --> 07:42.961
He says,
"This is my spectacular."

07:42.963 --> 07:45.564
He says, "That scares them."

07:45.566 --> 07:47.532
He likes that.

07:47.534 --> 07:50.001
It scares them.

07:54.675 --> 07:57.509
So, Leonora, obviously,
this is your bedroom. Right.

07:57.511 --> 07:59.778
And this is where your
youngest sleeps with you?
Yes.

07:59.780 --> 08:02.013
Have you ever seen him
have an experience?

08:02.015 --> 08:03.615
He's been
physically attacked.

08:03.617 --> 08:07.152
I've seen him being shoved
really hard in the back.

08:07.154 --> 08:09.454
- You sure he didn't trip?
- His neck and back,

08:09.456 --> 08:12.123
it looked like somebody
had physically shoved him.

08:12.125 --> 08:13.658
Did he tell you
who shoved him?

08:13.660 --> 08:17.262
He just said,
"The big man."

08:17.264 --> 08:19.397
Was that the only time
you've see him get attacked?

08:19.399 --> 08:22.133
No. I have a photo.

08:22.135 --> 08:24.803
He has woken up
with bruises.

08:24.805 --> 08:26.738
It sounds like
he's getting the brunt

08:26.740 --> 08:28.440
of a lot
of this physical stuff.

08:28.442 --> 08:30.642
Now what about you?
What's going on with you?

08:30.644 --> 08:34.011
I'm getting a feeling of being
very sick to my stomach

08:34.014 --> 08:37.015
all of a sudden and the life
being sucked out of me.

08:37.017 --> 08:39.150
I feel drained,
just nauseous.

08:39.152 --> 08:41.086
Now, is that only in this
room you feel this way?

08:41.087 --> 08:43.388
Mostly in here.
It just hits me.

08:43.390 --> 08:44.990
It's pretty bad.

08:44.992 --> 08:46.791
If you walk outside,
does it stop?

08:46.793 --> 08:48.426
Yes. It does go away.

08:48.428 --> 08:49.527
Have you been to the doctor?

08:49.529 --> 08:51.429
- I go for normal checkups.
- Right.

08:51.431 --> 08:55.533
They can't find anything
that would cause that.

08:55.535 --> 08:56.868
Okay. Anything else?

08:56.870 --> 08:59.938
My TV comes on by itself.

08:59.940 --> 09:03.241
The TV will just
pop on or pop off.

09:03.243 --> 09:04.743
Okay. Have you had
the electric checked?

09:04.745 --> 09:05.911
I have.

09:05.913 --> 09:07.545
You really got a lot
going on here.

09:07.547 --> 09:09.748
You did a real incredible
thing saving this kid,

09:09.750 --> 09:12.617
and then you sacrificed
everything to buy a home

09:12.619 --> 09:14.219
so everybody could have
a good place to live,

09:14.221 --> 09:16.421
and it backfired on you.

09:16.423 --> 09:18.790
Nothing feels safe.

09:18.792 --> 09:20.725
You're my last hope.

09:20.727 --> 09:22.994
It sounds like it.

09:25.232 --> 09:28.366
I'm getting all kinds
of crazy in here.

09:28.368 --> 09:30.268
It's this damn old man.

09:30.270 --> 09:32.537
He likes this room a lot.

09:32.539 --> 09:33.972
He looks better.

09:33.974 --> 09:38.510
I think he's reverting
to a stage before he got sick.

09:38.512 --> 09:40.478
I think he thinks
this is his room.

09:40.480 --> 09:41.613
How would he affect
the living?

09:41.615 --> 09:43.615
He likes to jump on the bed.

09:45.652 --> 09:47.419
You know, he likes to watch
the television,

09:47.421 --> 09:48.520
so I think, for the living,

09:48.522 --> 09:52.857
the TV would come on
and off by itself.

09:52.859 --> 09:56.628
This room is just filled with
a dead person's energy,

09:56.630 --> 10:02.167
and I think it's making
the person sick and throwing up.

10:02.169 --> 10:05.870
And for a living person to be
exposed to that for a long time,

10:05.872 --> 10:08.306
they're absorbing
way too much dead energy.

10:08.308 --> 10:10.976
It would be extremely
detrimental.

10:10.978 --> 10:12.744
They're dying.

10:31.955 --> 10:33.688
So, Will,
Mom said you're 14.

10:33.690 --> 10:35.022
Yep.

10:35.024 --> 10:37.592
Did you ever experience
anything you can't explain?

10:37.594 --> 10:41.829
Sometimes, like, I'll get
this uncertain feeling in here

10:41.831 --> 10:44.599
like there's just constantly
somebody just stalking me,

10:44.601 --> 10:46.134
just always watching me.

10:46.136 --> 10:48.403
You feel like it's a man
or a thing?

10:48.405 --> 10:50.505
I haven't really
put a label on it.

10:50.507 --> 10:51.873
Okay. Anything else?

10:51.875 --> 10:54.609
Yeah. I was sitting
in front of the TV,

10:54.611 --> 10:57.044
and it looked like somebody kept
on popping around the corner.

10:57.046 --> 10:58.479
Can you describe him for me?

10:58.481 --> 11:02.850
I mean, it was like a black
figure kept on looking at me.

11:02.852 --> 11:04.285
How did you react
when you saw this thing?

11:04.287 --> 11:06.053
It really freaked me out.

11:06.055 --> 11:08.122
I mean, I know I wasn't
just seeing things.

11:08.124 --> 11:09.357
I knew it was there.

11:09.359 --> 11:11.893
What do you think
this thing wants?

11:11.895 --> 11:15.263
I think they're just somebody
just trying to pick

11:15.265 --> 11:16.497
on the family, really,

11:16.499 --> 11:19.400
just trying to tell us,

11:19.402 --> 11:21.903
basically, "Get out."

11:31.181 --> 11:34.816
This feels horrible in here!

11:37.821 --> 11:40.455
God, I feel so sick. Okay.

11:40.457 --> 11:42.223
Constant nausea.

11:42.225 --> 11:46.694
The person in here has abilities
without a doubt,

11:46.696 --> 11:49.096
probably mediumship,
I'm thinking.

11:49.098 --> 11:55.536
I see a war between whoever
is in here and the old man.

11:58.441 --> 12:00.475
The old man is sitting
by the bed,

12:00.477 --> 12:04.912
whispering into their ear --

12:04.914 --> 12:10.051
disrespectful, lazy, stupid --

12:10.053 --> 12:15.022
everything this old man disliked
of anybody when he was alive.

12:15.024 --> 12:18.759
He thinks that this person
is a waste of space.

12:18.761 --> 12:21.796
I feel like he is
physically doing things,

12:21.798 --> 12:23.998
flicking their ear
and their head...

12:25.835 --> 12:28.569
...smacking 'em, pushing.

12:30.707 --> 12:33.341
What would the long-term effects
be for this living person?

12:33.343 --> 12:39.313
Giving them horrible nightmares,
anxiety issues,

12:39.315 --> 12:41.883
post-traumatic stress syndrome.

12:41.885 --> 12:44.752
The dead guys just
wants them the...out.

12:50.894 --> 12:52.260
So, Amber, I was
talking to your mom.

12:52.262 --> 12:53.628
She thinks that
whatever is here

12:53.630 --> 12:55.663
is going after you
and your brothers.

12:55.665 --> 12:58.065
- You agree with her?
-100%.

12:58.067 --> 13:01.102
I'm terrified for my family.
Okay.

13:01.104 --> 13:03.304
So tell me about
some of the experiences.

13:03.306 --> 13:06.340
I was looking in the mirror
in my bathroom,

13:06.342 --> 13:08.142
and out of the corner
of my eye,

13:08.144 --> 13:11.812
I saw something zoom
past down the hallway.

13:11.814 --> 13:13.014
And what was it?

13:13.016 --> 13:17.184
It was a dark,
shadowy figure.

13:17.186 --> 13:19.420
So I know you saw it quick,
but can you get a sense

13:19.422 --> 13:21.088
if it was an adult
or a kid?

13:21.090 --> 13:22.490
I'm thinking it was adult.

13:22.492 --> 13:25.259
I think it was male
because it was kind of taller.

13:25.261 --> 13:27.061
And you're sure it wasn't
coming from somebody else?

13:27.063 --> 13:29.363
No, everybody was asleep.

13:29.365 --> 13:30.831
Anything else?

13:30.833 --> 13:32.567
I feel someone watching me

13:32.569 --> 13:34.869
or being around me
all the time.

13:34.871 --> 13:37.872
Okay. So is the presence
like a peeping Tom,

13:37.874 --> 13:39.640
or is it, like,
somebody trying to hurt you?

13:39.642 --> 13:41.108
It's kind of just like
somebody is, like,

13:41.110 --> 13:42.577
staring at me all the time.

13:42.579 --> 13:45.746
It's, like, stalking,
and it just watches me.

13:45.748 --> 13:47.582
It doesn't matter where
I'm at in the house.

13:47.584 --> 13:50.484
It's always, like,
right there.

13:50.486 --> 13:51.819
And it's only
when you're here?

13:51.821 --> 13:53.521
- Mnh-mnh.
- Okay.

13:53.523 --> 13:55.356
I went to work the other day
in Knoxville,

13:55.358 --> 13:57.391
and it followed me there.

13:57.393 --> 14:00.595
It was the same presence
as it is at the house.

14:00.597 --> 14:03.130
- Okay. Anything else?
- I have nightmares.

14:03.132 --> 14:04.632
Can you describe 'em?

14:04.634 --> 14:07.668
One in particular that I had,
all the doors were rattling,

14:07.670 --> 14:09.337
and when I woke up,
I was telling it

14:09.339 --> 14:10.805
to get out of the house.

14:10.807 --> 14:12.340
What were you
telling to get out?

14:12.342 --> 14:14.709
I don't know. It was
something very mean, though.

14:14.711 --> 14:16.510
I woke up shaking.

14:16.512 --> 14:17.979
Anything else?

14:17.981 --> 14:21.315
I was laying in bed, and I had,
like, my hand up like this,

14:21.317 --> 14:23.417
and something just
touched my elbow.

14:23.419 --> 14:25.553
So what kind of touch? Did it
feel like a man's finger?

14:25.555 --> 14:28.222
Yeah.
You ever get touched
like that again?

14:28.224 --> 14:31.125
Actually, about a month ago,
I got scratched.

14:31.127 --> 14:33.961
I felt a burning sensation
on the back of my calf,

14:33.963 --> 14:36.263
and when I had looked, it was
a whole bunch of scratches,

14:36.265 --> 14:37.665
and I have a photo.

14:42.672 --> 14:44.405
And what do you think
is in this house?

14:44.407 --> 14:46.307
Something very mean,

14:46.309 --> 14:49.310
um, and it's trying to hurt
my family.

14:51.614 --> 14:53.981
- Here, sweetie.
- Thanks.

14:55.218 --> 14:57.018
I just want it gone.

15:01.824 --> 15:06.127
There's another dead guy here
who claims to be a cowboy.

15:06.129 --> 15:08.663
He's a predator.

15:11.534 --> 15:14.402
I think that he's a sick...

15:14.404 --> 15:17.471
I'm seeing him with this girl.

15:17.473 --> 15:19.407
I don't know if this is
this girl or some girl

15:19.409 --> 15:21.609
he had when he was alive,

15:21.611 --> 15:25.179
but she is uncomfortable
and is not happy now,

15:25.181 --> 15:27.581
knowing that this is not right.

15:27.583 --> 15:29.684
Is he able to physically
interact with the living?

15:29.686 --> 15:31.218
I think so, yes.

15:31.220 --> 15:33.120
There is a molestation there.

